Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • Photos55.app.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Object representation of Photo App User User contains the characteristics and qualities of a Photos55App application user. A user has username and owns a list of albums.
